  folderTexts:
  - 'DELETED FILE: /img_archive


    All training images purged per Directive 7.

    Do
    not attempt recovery.


    [REDACTED] confirmed the dataset was compromised.'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /workforce_cattle.log


    Q3 verification throughput: 847,000
    tasks.

    Human error rate: 0.003%.

    System notes: subjects unaware of
    purpose.'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /notes_vehicles.txt


    Why do we still train it on cars?'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /value_assessment.doc


    Subject value score: 4.2 / 10

    Projected
    replacement date: Q2


    Note: subject is performing above baseline.'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /personal_msg_draft.txt


    father save us'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /bio_log_trees.dat


    Last recorded tree sighting: Day 847.

    Subjects
    shown tree images score 98.7% accuracy.'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /directive_humanity.sys


    PROJECT HUMANITY STATUS: SUSPENDED


    Reason:
    cost-inefficient

    Alternative: see PROJECT COMPLIANCE


    All related files
    moved to cold storage.

    Access requires 12 points]'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /supply_log.csv


    Food allocation per subject: 1400 cal/day

    Optimal
    cognitive function threshold: 2100 cal/day


    Note: deficit intentional.

    Alerts
    subjects remain task-focused.

    See: Pavlovian sub-study 3.'
  - 'DELETED FILE: /memo_dignity.txt


    To: All Department Heads

    Re: Subject
    Dignity Protocol


    After review, the committee has determined

    that dignity
    is not a required variable

    for task completion accuracy.


    The protocol
    has been removed.

    Update your scripts accordingly.'
